---
import PresDualCTA from "./PresDualCTA.astro";
---

<section class="pres-founder">
  <div class="pres-founder__container">
    <div class="pres-founder__content">
      <p class="pres-founder__eyebrow">Built by a person, not a fund</p>
      <h2 class="pres-founder__heading">Same person, every call.</h2>
      <p class="pres-founder__subhead">
        Joe Robert has been doing this for 25 years. 200 deals. $10 million raised from private
        investors. Every offering completed. Every payment made.
      </p>

      <ul class="pres-founder__stats">
        <li class="pres-founder__stat">
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-value">25+</span>
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-label">Years of experience</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pres-founder__stat">
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-value">100%</span>
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-label">Payments record</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pres-founder__stat">
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-value">$10M+</span>
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-label">Raised from private investors</span>
        </li>
        <li class="pres-founder__stat">
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-value">200+</span>
          <span class="pres-founder__stat-label">Properties sold</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pres-founder__align">
        <p class="pres-founder__align-eyebrow">Why I run this myself</p>
        <p class="pres-founder__align-body">
          For 25 years, my name has been on every deal. There is no committee to point to and no
          one else to call. The person who raises the capital is the same person who answers when
          you need something. Aligned by structure, not by promise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="pres-founder__close">
        When you call Robert Ventures, you do not get a script. You get a person who has answered
        this exact question for 25 years.
      </p>

      <PresDualCTA primary="call" location="founder" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-founder {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-founder__container {
    max-width: 1136px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pres-founder__content {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .pres-founder__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pres-founder__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .pres-founder__subhead {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .pres-founder__heading + .pres-founder__subhead {
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .pres-founder__stats,
  .pres-founder__align,
  .pres-founder__close {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pres-founder__stats {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 20px 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .pres-founder__stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .pres-founder__stat-value {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 100%;
    font-variant-numeric: lining-nums;
  }

  .pres-founder__stat-label {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 140%;
  }

  .pres-founder__align {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-brand);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .pres-founder__align-eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-founder__align-body {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 160%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-founder__close {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 150%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-founder__container {
      padding: 96px 32px;
    }

    .pres-founder__content {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pres-founder__heading {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }

    .pres-founder__stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }

    .pres-founder__stat-value {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pres-founder__container {
      padding: 120px 48px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-founder__heading {
      font-size: 3.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1920px) {
    .pres-founder__heading {
      font-size: 3.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
